I changed the sprites made the cache into dropbox compiled and jarred and for some reason it doesn’t update for new players. If you guys could help me i would be really thankfull.

If you’re trying to use the same cache name you’re an idiot. It’s not going to download the new cache if you upload a new, because it already reads the person has that cache. Just add the cache updater that’s been released a few times now. Good luck.
